folios.text:
Wb Dem Land ze magtlenburg
Cuinart fobe Rutt
Sictving hibzow
peter sin banful priuet
Wb Luterning
Jodt Don Garkwart Ratt
Dapravind de mirezwart priuet
toda Den Gayan sin Enuage
Wb Sctofen land
Jaled ni Rung
Gamb Rudesert
Femiend Gant
Wb Probstung
Gant Don Sempke sin priuet
pnt Jafong deiu
